1
00:01:40,811 --> 00:01:42,369
As a professional team,

2
00:01:42,569 --> 00:01:47,237
We'd like to change your works into a cartoon

3
00:01:47,437 --> 00:01:50,827
Mr.Shao,we trust your professional skills

4
00:01:51,027 --> 00:01:56,127
But I wonder why you chose this piece of work

5
00:01:56,327 --> 00:01:58,937
Actually,over these years,

6
00:01:59,137 --> 00:02:00,487
I always have a dream

7
00:02:00,687 --> 00:02:04,340
It's to film a cartoon belonging to myself

8
00:02:04,540 --> 00:02:08,221
Yishan's works let me see the hope of Chinese comics

9
00:02:09,816 --> 00:02:10,606
In that way

10
00:02:16,666 --> 00:02:20,520
Maybe we should discuss how to distribute profits now

11
00:02:22,236 --> 00:02:23,166
Manager Xiang

12
00:02:44,459 --> 00:02:47,019
You can be assured of that

13
00:02:47,219 --> 00:02:50,011
After all,we all want to achieve our goals

14
00:02:50,536 --> 00:02:53,020
We have no intention to refuse you

15
00:03:08,000 --> 00:03:18,640
We heard that you hired Xiang Zeyi who once copied this works of ours

16
00:03:19,780 --> 00:03:22,930
I wonder if it's true

17
00:03:25,273 --> 00:03:26,240
You don't have to worry

18
00:03:26,652 --> 00:03:27,982
About that

19
00:03:28,182 --> 00:03:31,456
Xiang Zeyi messed up our cooperation with an overseas team

20
00:03:31,656 --> 00:03:34,115
We fired him long time ago

21
00:03:35,770 --> 00:03:39,910
OK then,I hope we can have a good cooperation

22
00:03:46,563 --> 00:03:48,720
Am I fired?

23
00:03:49,910 --> 00:03:53,020
Xiang Zeyi, meet you again

24
00:03:53,030 --> 00:03:53,556
Calm down first

25
00:03:54,419 --> 00:03:55,618
Why is he here

26
00:03:58,460 --> 00:04:01,530
Xiang Zeyi,I've treated you very well

27
00:04:02,082 --> 00:04:03,979
We have nothing to say

28
00:04:04,770 --> 00:04:05,516
I helped you

29
00:04:06,490 --> 00:04:08,003
But I can't always help you

30
00:04:09,750 --> 00:04:10,323
Now

31
00:04:11,020 --> 00:04:14,023
I've found a better choice

32
00:04:15,486 --> 00:04:16,736
You should know that enough is enough

33
00:04:29,377 --> 00:04:30,417
Shao Jia

34
00:04:34,186 --> 00:04:35,943
I trusted you so much

35
00:04:39,036 --> 00:04:40,753
But I think I was wrong about you

36
00:04:45,180 --> 00:04:45,706
Mr.Shao

37
00:04:46,510 --> 00:04:47,270
Are you okay?

38
00:04:47,390 --> 00:04:47,890
It's okay

39
00:04:49,313 --> 00:04:50,343
Just small things

40
00:04:51,113 --> 00:04:55,040
We'll discuss our later cooperation with overseas team

41
00:04:55,980 --> 00:04:56,480
Wish us a good cooperation

42
00:04:56,490 --> 00:04:57,696
OK,we are about to leave

43
00:04:58,416 --> 00:04:58,916
This way

44
00:05:03,100 --> 00:05:07,780
Thanks for what did not kill me
For it made me stronger

45
00:05:16,520 --> 00:05:17,300
Why?

46
00:05:20,640 --> 00:05:21,620
Why!

47
00:05:25,240 --> 00:05:25,960
Zeyi

48
00:05:28,893 --> 00:05:31,229
I've studied painting for so many years

49
00:05:32,840 --> 00:05:37,370
For what?

50
00:05:46,450 --> 00:05:47,380
You tell me

51
00:05:51,080 --> 00:05:52,896
I trusted him so much

52
00:05:55,516 --> 00:05:57,513
Why did he do this to me?

53
00:05:58,780 --> 00:06:01,393
Zeyi, calm down first

54
00:06:01,990 --> 00:06:03,933
Maybe it's not like what you are thinking

55
00:06:07,260 --> 00:06:08,740
I heard it myself

56
00:06:12,400 --> 00:06:15,200
He chose Gu Yishan who ruined my life over me

57
00:06:20,380 --> 00:06:21,400
Gu Yishan

58
00:06:24,513 --> 00:06:26,136
Gu Yishan

59
00:06:28,803 --> 00:06:34,120
Maybe Mr.Shao has other reasons

60
00:06:43,110 --> 00:06:43,610
Zeyi

61
00:06:46,146 --> 00:06:47,823
I think too highly of myself

62
00:06:49,900 --> 00:06:52,940
Stay away from me!

63
00:06:58,660 --> 00:07:02,420
I thought I could prove myself through working hard

64
00:07:07,180 --> 00:07:07,940
At last

65
00:07:23,506 --> 00:07:25,670
I am a loser

66
00:07:29,760 --> 00:07:32,660
Zeyi, listen to me

67
00:07:33,520 --> 00:07:35,560
You are not a loser at all

68
00:07:36,760 --> 00:07:38,260
I have belief in you

69
00:07:42,490 --> 00:07:45,813
Leave me alone

70
00:07:51,980 --> 00:07:52,800
It's all in vain

71
00:07:55,880 --> 00:07:58,460
I tried so hard to prove myself

72
00:08:02,140 --> 00:08:04,240
To get rid of that nightmare

73
00:08:10,210 --> 00:08:10,963
In the end

74
00:08:15,786 --> 00:08:18,503
I still get defeated by him

75
00:08:24,976 --> 00:08:26,663
He ruined me!

76
00:09:16,463 --> 00:09:17,360
Let me introduce to you

77
00:09:18,486 --> 00:09:22,163
This is Mr Jinshang who's in charge of overseas programs

78
00:09:22,963 --> 00:09:26,120
This is Mr Gu Huai, the director of Sanzhou Press

79
00:09:28,433 --> 00:09:32,956
That is Mr Gu Yishan, the original painter of this comics

80
00:09:38,760 --> 00:09:39,910
Can we start now?

81
00:09:41,183 --> 00:09:43,130
Wait a moment

82
00:09:43,660 --> 00:09:45,270
There's a little change

83
00:09:45,300 --> 00:09:46,523
I invited one of my friend to this meeting

84
00:09:47,523 --> 00:09:51,146
Please wait for a moment, thank you

85
00:09:51,640 --> 00:09:57,550
Mr.Shao, we never agreed that anyone else can attend this meeting

86
00:09:58,853 --> 00:10:01,856
This is a rude thing to do

87
00:10:03,933 --> 00:10:05,110
Please calm down

88
00:10:06,286 --> 00:10:09,546
We all want to make a deal

89
00:10:10,556 --> 00:10:16,046
Just wait a moment
I believe my friend will be helpful to this project

90
00:10:29,540 --> 00:10:30,270
Wenjie

91
00:10:35,833 --> 00:10:38,680
Xiang Zeyi, what are you doing here?

92
00:10:46,990 --> 00:10:48,716
We are here to reveal what you are

93
00:10:51,723 --> 00:10:53,786
Yu, it's you

94
00:10:55,323 --> 00:10:56,600
We're here to testify

95
00:10:58,696 --> 00:11:01,013
The three of us are all witnesses

96
00:11:01,600 --> 00:11:07,100
We can prove that Xiang Zeyi didn't copy any works

97
00:11:09,990 --> 00:11:11,956
What do you mean?

98
00:11:14,630 --> 00:11:16,753
Just sit down and listen

99
00:11:18,333 --> 00:11:19,580
Sit down, Xiang Zeyi

100
00:11:27,186 --> 00:11:29,166
Editor Yu, you may start now

101
00:11:35,963 --> 00:11:39,713
This is a draft from Xiang Zeyi

102
00:11:41,463 --> 00:11:43,666
This is the comics from Gu Yishan which is about to be published

103
00:11:44,716 --> 00:11:46,020
You can compare these two

104
00:11:49,363 --> 00:11:50,786
So what?

105
00:11:52,673 --> 00:11:56,450
Xiang Zeyi probably imitated my style

106
00:11:58,416 --> 00:12:00,760
He's just a thief

107
00:12:03,556 --> 00:12:04,290
Gu Yishan

108
00:12:05,380 --> 00:12:07,790
Shame on you

109
00:12:08,083 --> 00:12:09,176
After all these years

110
00:12:09,440 --> 00:12:11,856
you still don't dare to admit
that you are the one who copied from him

111
00:12:12,163 --> 00:12:16,213
If you really drew this,
draw one right now

112
00:12:21,176 --> 00:12:23,326
This bastard ruined me

113
00:12:24,780 --> 00:12:25,863
I blame him

114
00:12:26,153 --> 00:12:30,050
I was so talented

115
00:12:30,890 --> 00:12:34,963
But my hands were ruined by him

116
00:12:35,696 --> 00:12:36,563
I can't draw now

117
00:12:39,400 --> 00:12:40,320
It's all your fault

118
00:12:46,376 --> 00:12:48,656
Gu Yishan, calm down

119
00:12:50,510 --> 00:12:52,950
Maybe we can't prove Xiang Zeyi is the painter

120
00:12:53,396 --> 00:12:56,476
Maybe we made up all the evidence

121
00:12:57,203 --> 00:13:03,493
But now there's one person who can prove that you didn't made the comics

122
00:13:07,596 --> 00:13:08,096
Who?

123
00:13:09,640 --> 00:13:10,146
Me

124
00:13:16,406 --> 00:13:20,240
Everyone perceives the world in different way

125
00:13:21,846 --> 00:13:22,906
The reason is

126
00:13:26,883 --> 00:13:30,040
Everyone has different sense about colors

127
00:13:31,516 --> 00:13:33,176
Editor Yu, am I right?

128
00:13:34,210 --> 00:13:34,753
Right

129
00:13:35,780 --> 00:13:38,260
The drawing style can be imitated

130
00:13:38,913 --> 00:13:42,730
But the feeling for colors is unique

131
00:13:45,260 --> 00:13:51,370
I agree, we can't copy any of that

132
00:13:53,560 --> 00:13:56,236
Mr.Jingshang should be our witness

133
00:13:57,806 --> 00:14:00,540
My nephew still can't draw

134
00:14:01,520 --> 00:14:05,090
How can you prove his innocence?

135
00:14:05,583 --> 00:14:06,223
That's right

136
00:14:08,443 --> 00:14:10,190
I can't draw now

137
00:14:11,633 --> 00:14:13,366
How can I prove?

138
00:14:16,180 --> 00:14:16,956
Don't worry

139
00:14:17,586 --> 00:14:19,546
We won't ask you to draw

140
00:14:24,410 --> 00:14:25,073
Gu Yishan

141
00:14:26,000 --> 00:14:29,490
Do you know the prominent feature of this collection?

142
00:14:39,560 --> 00:14:40,333
The work I did is very nice

143
00:15:19,410 --> 00:15:22,260
You've been lying to me for all these years

144
00:15:22,816 --> 00:15:25,900
Wait, let me explain

145
00:15:44,990 --> 00:15:45,490
Don't worry

146
00:15:49,540 --> 00:15:50,373
Let's go

147
00:15:52,060 --> 00:15:54,016
You go ahead
I have something to deal with

148
00:15:56,776 --> 00:15:57,276
OK

149
00:16:24,896 --> 00:16:25,446
Mr.Shao

150
00:16:28,336 --> 00:16:29,023
Mr.Xiang

151
00:16:32,766 --> 00:16:36,450
I apologize for what I did before

152
00:16:37,833 --> 00:16:38,380
I'm sorry

153
00:16:41,190 --> 00:16:44,956
I believe that we can continue our cooperation

154
00:17:00,996 --> 00:17:02,456
I've been learning painting since I was a kid

155
00:17:05,040 --> 00:17:05,863
I love it

156
00:17:09,566 --> 00:17:14,100
I believe I can express my feelings to this world in the most direct way

157
00:17:18,520 --> 00:17:20,353
After what I have gone through,

158
00:17:22,600 --> 00:17:26,500
I was so depressed and thought of giving up

159
00:17:28,753 --> 00:17:30,486
At that time I even couldn't  tell what is beauty

160
00:17:31,340 --> 00:17:32,406
What is ugliness

161
00:17:34,840 --> 00:17:35,876
You may think

162
00:17:39,063 --> 00:17:45,530
Someone like me who made such a big mistake don't deserve a good life

163
00:17:45,786 --> 00:17:50,463
I still had the same thought like you this morning

164
00:17:51,536 --> 00:17:54,366
But I figured it out just now

165
00:17:59,580 --> 00:18:00,646
I should thank you

166
00:18:04,256 --> 00:18:06,833
I should thank that miserable experience

167
00:18:09,663 --> 00:18:11,340
It made me try harder

168
00:18:12,773 --> 00:18:13,736
More persistent

169
00:18:15,100 --> 00:18:17,933
And find out what I really want

170
00:18:22,983 --> 00:18:26,520
This project means a lot to me

171
00:18:28,836 --> 00:18:34,576
I believe you understand how many efforts it takes a creator to gain recognition

172
00:18:37,480 --> 00:18:39,456
You denied my team

173
00:18:41,790 --> 00:18:43,303
Just because of my mistake

174
00:18:44,420 --> 00:18:45,163
Mr.Jinshang

175
00:18:47,316 --> 00:18:48,400
I always believe

176
00:18:49,266 --> 00:18:54,186
Everyone who treat life and work seriously
should be respected by others

177
00:18:55,856 --> 00:19:01,086
I hope that we can respect each other in the later cooperation

178
00:19:02,713 --> 00:19:03,383
Mr.Xiang

179
00:19:04,383 --> 00:19:06,463
I'm impressed by your courage

180
00:19:07,443 --> 00:19:09,113
And I admire your talent

181
00:19:11,056 --> 00:19:13,580
I believe we can carry on our cooperation

182
00:19:14,663 --> 00:19:15,900
Like you said

183
00:19:16,743 --> 00:19:19,880
Understanding and respecting each other

184
00:19:30,526 --> 00:19:31,050
Fighting

185
00:19:37,373 --> 00:19:38,020
Thanks

186
00:20:18,230 --> 00:20:19,780
What's your plan for future?

187
00:20:22,363 --> 00:20:26,750
I feel relieved after proving Xiang Zeyi is innocent

188
00:20:28,386 --> 00:20:29,716
I'm not sure about my future plan

189
00:20:29,940 --> 00:20:32,226
Get married and have a child I guess

190
00:20:33,213 --> 00:20:34,416
Start a new life

191
00:20:35,770 --> 00:20:38,313
Actually have you ever thought about

192
00:20:40,003 --> 00:20:41,086
After this

193
00:20:41,686 --> 00:20:43,166
I've figured it out

194
00:20:44,143 --> 00:20:46,923
I owe you and him too much

195
00:20:47,570 --> 00:20:49,236
I shouldn't keep bothering you

196
00:20:50,170 --> 00:20:51,300
How about you?

197
00:20:52,760 --> 00:20:53,286
Me?

198
00:20:54,450 --> 00:20:56,626
You should make a decision

199
00:20:56,953 --> 00:20:59,380
What do you think of your relationship with him?

200
00:21:02,660 --> 00:21:03,406
I don't know yet

201
00:21:05,890 --> 00:21:07,116
We're silly

202
00:21:08,300 --> 00:21:12,153
We fell in love with the same man for so many years

203
00:21:13,276 --> 00:21:16,476
Sometimes I think it's very silly of us

204
00:21:32,220 --> 00:21:35,740
Xiang Zeyi, you idiot

205
00:21:39,256 --> 00:21:39,993
Your turn

206
00:21:41,160 --> 00:21:45,640
Xiang Zeyi, I don't like you anymore

207
00:21:50,920 --> 00:21:52,000
Doctor Lin

208
00:21:54,920 --> 00:21:55,700
What's going on?

209
00:21:56,396 --> 00:21:57,490
Don't worry

210
00:21:57,540 --> 00:22:00,406
Doctor Wu has arranged further diagnosis

211
00:22:00,436 --> 00:22:01,750
The result will come out soon

212
00:22:02,323 --> 00:22:03,683
It's just

213
00:22:03,713 --> 00:22:04,486
Don't worry about me

214
00:22:05,030 --> 00:22:07,530
I've been prepared

215
00:22:07,896 --> 00:22:09,883
Just tell me the truth
I can handle it

216
00:22:11,510 --> 00:22:12,803
OK

217
00:22:13,840 --> 00:22:14,873
I'll tell you the truth

218
00:22:16,886 --> 00:22:21,430
According to the earlier result,
we think it may be Alzheimer's Disease

219
00:22:23,146 --> 00:22:23,750
What is it?

220
00:22:25,466 --> 00:22:30,053
It's normally called dementia

221
00:22:33,760 --> 00:22:34,586
Uncle

222
00:22:35,523 --> 00:22:36,963
According to her current state

223
00:22:37,073 --> 00:22:40,413
Will she forget us one day?

224
00:22:45,290 --> 00:22:49,280
According to her physical condition,
it's only the first stage

225
00:22:49,486 --> 00:22:51,746
If we take good care of her

226
00:22:52,186 --> 00:22:54,323
Her decline in memory can be controlled

227
00:22:55,856 --> 00:22:57,793
I will take good care of her

228
00:22:59,180 --> 00:23:00,896
She can't forget us

229
00:23:16,886 --> 00:23:18,913
Honey

230
00:23:19,306 --> 00:23:23,233
If our baby is like that,
will you be annoyed?

231
00:23:23,893 --> 00:23:26,340
No, I love kids

232
00:23:33,163 --> 00:23:35,136
I thought you don't want kids

233
00:23:36,166 --> 00:23:39,006
I never said that

234
00:23:39,990 --> 00:23:42,623
You said it before

235
00:23:43,380 --> 00:23:49,360
You said you want to build a career before having kids

236
00:23:50,250 --> 00:23:56,700
You told me that you want to enjoy your life

237
00:23:57,153 --> 00:23:59,540
That's why I said that

238
00:24:00,606 --> 00:24:03,146
I didn't mean that

239
00:24:03,233 --> 00:24:07,740
I love kids, I said that for your career

240
00:24:13,763 --> 00:24:16,426
I was wrong the whole time

241
00:24:19,650 --> 00:24:20,193
Honey

242
00:24:21,216 --> 00:24:25,840
I think kids should be the fruit of love

243
00:24:26,980 --> 00:24:30,730
We should let it be

244
00:24:33,430 --> 00:24:34,396
We can't do that on purpose

245
00:24:43,973 --> 00:24:45,236
Honey, actually

246
00:24:52,013 --> 00:24:53,500
I have something to tell you

247
00:24:54,790 --> 00:24:55,290
Go ahead

248
00:25:00,860 --> 00:25:01,603
I'm pregnant

249
00:25:03,916 --> 00:25:04,620
What?

250
00:25:05,058 --> 00:25:09,189
I'm carrying our baby

251
00:25:17,748 --> 00:25:18,455
Really?

252
00:25:28,696 --> 00:25:29,650
It's still early

253
00:25:31,513 --> 00:25:35,120
Only one month

254
00:25:39,260 --> 00:25:39,856
Honey

255
00:25:45,713 --> 00:25:46,763
Thank you honey

256
00:26:11,793 --> 00:26:12,800
Mom, what's wrong?

257
00:26:13,203 --> 00:26:15,210
Come back for dinner tonight

258
00:26:15,580 --> 00:26:16,860
Don't forget

259
00:26:17,193 --> 00:26:18,386
I made something delicious for you

260
00:26:18,676 --> 00:26:20,713
You've told me, mom

261
00:26:21,240 --> 00:26:23,043
I promise I'll come

262
00:26:23,680 --> 00:26:24,396
Bye

263
00:26:35,306 --> 00:26:36,676
What's going on with my mom?

264
00:26:37,156 --> 00:26:38,943
This is the fifth call

265
00:26:51,553 --> 00:26:53,260
I thought we would have dinner at my home tonight

266
00:26:54,100 --> 00:26:55,276
Why do you ask me here?

267
00:26:58,213 --> 00:26:59,540
I have to tell you something

268
00:27:10,066 --> 00:27:11,753
You should understand them

269
00:27:12,190 --> 00:27:13,880
They didn't tell you because they don't want you to worry

270
00:27:15,586 --> 00:27:18,990
What can we do now?

271
00:27:19,530 --> 00:27:20,610
Listen to me

272
00:27:21,303 --> 00:27:23,060
It's still the first stage

273
00:27:23,526 --> 00:27:26,970
If you can take good care of her,
she won't get worse

274
00:27:28,266 --> 00:27:28,766
OK

275
00:27:41,353 --> 00:27:42,173
Eat more

276
00:27:43,050 --> 00:27:43,570
Sen

277
00:27:44,016 --> 00:27:46,123
Are you tired from studying?

278
00:27:46,506 --> 00:27:47,673
Look at you, you are so skinny

279
00:27:47,750 --> 00:27:48,250
Come on

280
00:27:48,686 --> 00:27:51,496
Aunt,I've been working out recently
I can't eat too much

281
00:27:52,626 --> 00:27:55,163
OK, you can have less

282
00:27:59,453 --> 00:28:02,210
Yezi, listen to me

283
00:28:03,116 --> 00:28:10,626
Don't focus too much on work, you'll be 30 soon

284
00:28:11,316 --> 00:28:15,936
You should consider your future

285
00:28:16,363 --> 00:28:22,290
If you want to find a husband, you should find someone like Sen

286
00:28:23,543 --> 00:28:25,726
So reliable

287
00:28:26,720 --> 00:28:30,273
We should not talk while having food
Just eat

288
00:28:32,753 --> 00:28:34,590
Come on, have some meat

289
00:28:35,690 --> 00:28:36,433
It's okay, dad

290
00:28:37,573 --> 00:28:39,963
I want to hear my mom talking

291
00:28:46,916 --> 00:28:51,036
Yezi, I know that

292
00:28:51,720 --> 00:28:53,420
You don't want to hear my chatter

293
00:28:55,376 --> 00:28:58,706
But I still want to tell you

294
00:29:00,990 --> 00:29:04,700
That your mom and dad are getting older

295
00:29:05,226 --> 00:29:11,533
We will leave you some day

296
00:29:13,396 --> 00:29:25,976
When that day comes,
you are the only one we can't let go of

297
00:29:29,216 --> 00:29:36,013
We want nothing else after all these years' hard working

298
00:29:37,063 --> 00:29:41,660
We just want you to live a good life

299
00:29:42,533 --> 00:29:46,173
We'll feel satisfied if you are happy

300
00:29:49,090 --> 00:30:02,460
When it occurs to me that we will leave some day

301
00:30:03,400 --> 00:30:08,293
And you are still alone

302
00:30:09,306 --> 00:30:16,703
How can we rest assured?

303
00:30:30,790 --> 00:30:33,226
What am I doing?

304
00:30:34,790 --> 00:30:36,270
I'm really getting old

305
00:30:36,440 --> 00:30:39,210
I can't even control my tears

306
00:30:41,600 --> 00:30:43,130
Don't laugh at me, Sen

307
00:30:44,860 --> 00:30:47,410
Let's eat

308
00:30:48,340 --> 00:30:48,860
Let's eat

309
00:30:53,856 --> 00:30:54,993
What happened to you?

310
00:31:00,366 --> 00:31:02,296
What's wrong, sweetheart

311
00:31:03,600 --> 00:31:06,186
It's all my fault

312
00:31:18,843 --> 00:31:19,393
You were looking for me

313
00:31:20,503 --> 00:31:21,130
Let's take a walk

314
00:31:33,553 --> 00:31:35,470
We shouldn't keep silent

315
00:31:36,416 --> 00:31:37,243
Just tell me what you want to say

316
00:31:43,466 --> 00:31:47,880
I've been thinking a lot lately

317
00:31:49,780 --> 00:31:53,933
I'm clear that we have to make a choice one day

318
00:31:59,296 --> 00:31:59,990
What choice?

319
00:32:02,840 --> 00:32:04,203
Everything has been settled

320
00:32:05,796 --> 00:32:08,960
We should face each other now

321
00:32:18,500 --> 00:32:23,590
Until now, I haven't figured out what I am thinking

322
00:32:28,526 --> 00:32:29,073
Zeyi

323
00:32:34,866 --> 00:32:39,170
To tell the truth, have you ever thought we are no longer young

324
00:32:40,563 --> 00:32:45,730
We can't have the relationship we had in college

325
00:32:47,673 --> 00:32:50,670
We feel so stressed out

326
00:32:50,760 --> 00:32:53,086
But you are still with me, right?

327
00:33:03,073 --> 00:33:04,196
You know what

328
00:33:06,470 --> 00:33:11,500
I feel so confused after talking to my mom

329
00:33:13,520 --> 00:33:15,060
I can't even imagine

330
00:33:16,983 --> 00:33:19,943
what we will be like when we get old

331
00:33:25,356 --> 00:33:26,106
Don't think too much

332
00:33:30,343 --> 00:33:31,373
Everything will be alright

333
00:33:33,240 --> 00:33:34,453
Don't leave yourself too much pressure

334
00:33:35,423 --> 00:33:36,520
But I am worried

335
00:33:38,350 --> 00:33:41,746
Recently, my mom

336
00:33:44,166 --> 00:33:46,256
She can't even remember who I am

337
00:33:48,170 --> 00:33:49,446
which makes me feel more upset

338
00:34:04,576 --> 00:34:05,076
Yezi

339
00:34:10,920 --> 00:34:11,620
I'm okay
